<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8209497>
    dc:description "FIGURE 32. Phaloria (Phaloria) rotundata sp. nov. ♁ genitalia in dorsal (A), ventral (B) and lateral (C) views. Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
